OL,3,CParents jailed over death of five-week-
OL,4,Cold baby with 40 rib fractures
OL,6,FThis article contains details that
OL,7,Fsome readers may find distressing
OL,9,FA father who murdered his five-week-
OL,10,Fold daughter by causing her a brain
OL,11,Finjury and more than 40 rib fractures
OL,12,Fin repeated assaults when he lost his
OL,13,Ftemper has been jailed for life.
OL,15,FBoth of baby Darcy-Leigh Jefferson's
OL,16,Flegs were also fractured in the 10
OL,17,Fdays before she died on March 29th,
OL,18,F2022, a seven-week trial at Stafford
OL,19,FCrown Court heard.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
