PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776442271
OL,3,CParents jailed over death of five-week-
OL,4,Cold baby with 40 rib fractures
OL,6,FHer father, 35-year-old Sean
OL,7,FJefferson, who was found guilty of
OL,8,Fmurder and two counts of causing
OL,9,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent, was
OL,10,Fhanded a minimum term of 22 years on
OL,11,FThursday (April 16th).
OL,13,FDarcy-Leigh's mother, Amy Clark, 34,
OL,14,Fwas found guilty of causing or
OL,15,Fallowing the death of a child and two
OL,16,Fcounts of causing or allowing serious
OL,17,Fharm to a child after charges of
OL,18,Fmurder and manslaughter against her
OL,19,Fwere dropped by prosecutors during the
OL,20,Ftrial.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776442271
OL,3,CParents jailed over death of five-week-
OL,4,Cold baby with 40 rib fractures
OL,6,FClark, who was cleared of two counts
OL,7,Fof causing grievous bodily harm with
OL,8,Fintent, was sentenced to seven years
OL,9,Fin prison.
OL,11,FSentencing Jefferson, of Walsall,
OL,12,Fjudge Mrs Justice Brunner KC said:
OL,13,F"The death of a young child is a
OL,14,Fterrible tragedy. Darcy-Leigh should
OL,15,Fhave had a long life being loved by
OL,16,Fher family and friends.
OL,18,F"You have deprived her of her life and
OL,19,Fyou have deprived others the pleasure
OL,20,Fof getting to know her and sharing
OL,21,Ftheir life."
OL,26,@uD@AOUzD@AOU}D@LO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776442271
OL,3,CParents jailed over death of five-week-
OL,4,Cold baby with 40 rib fractures
OL,6,FShe added: "As her father, you had
OL,7,Fsignificant caring responsibilities
OL,8,Fand you were a person she was entitled
OL,9,Fto look to for love and protection."
OL,11,FThe judge said she was satisfied that
OL,12,FJefferson lost his temper when he
OL,13,Finflicted the injuries on his baby.
OL,26,@nD@LOUqD@dO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
