OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776442271
OL,3,CParents jailed over death of five-week-
OL,4,Cold baby with 40 rib fractures
OL,6,FThe trial heard Darcy-Leigh, who was
OL,7,Fborn five weeks premature on February
OL,8,F20 2022, had been "physically
OL,9,Fassaulted on a repeated basis" and had
OL,10,Fa total of 47 rib fractures when she
OL,11,Fdied of a brain injury two days after
OL,12,Fbeing taken to hospital on March 27
OL,13,Fthat year.
OL,15,FWhen Darcy-Leigh was born by caesarean
OL,16,Fsection just weeks before, she weighed
OL,17,Fabout four pounds.
OL,26,@pD@SOUqD@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776442271
OL,3,CParents jailed over death of five-week-
OL,4,Cold baby with 40 rib fractures
OL,6,FProsecution counsel Harpreet Sandhu KC
OL,7,Fsaid the "catastrophic" injury to
OL,8,FDarcy-Leigh's head had been caused by
OL,9,Fher being shaken violently or having
OL,10,Fher head struck against a surface.
OL,12,FThe court heard the fatal attack must
OL,13,Fhave taken place between 7am and
OL,14,F7.18am on March 27 after Jefferson
OL,15,Ftook Darcy-Leigh downstairs at their
OL,16,Fformer home in Hudson Drive in
OL,17,FBurntwood in Staffordshire.
OL,26,@oD@JOUoD@WO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
