SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776442271
OL,3,CParents jailed over death of five-week-
OL,4,Cold baby with 40 rib fractures
OL,6,FRichard Atkins KC, defending
OL,7,FJefferson, said the murder was not
OL,8,Fpremeditated, adding: "What happened
OL,9,Fwould have happened through temper and
OL,10,Ffrustration."
OL,12,FCredit: Staffordshire Police
OL,14,FThis is the moment a killer father
OL,15,Fthreatened to report two police
OL,16,Fofficers after his "hand was hurt" as
OL,17,Fhe was put in handcuffs.
OL,26,@pD@WOUrD@MO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
