PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776442271
OL,3,CParents jailed over death of five-week-
OL,4,Cold baby with 40 rib fractures
OL,6,FDuring the trial, Mr Sandhu told the
OL,7,Fjury Clark was living at a "tidy and
OL,8,Fwell-presented" home and gave the
OL,9,Fimpression of being a mother who was
OL,10,Fin control while hiding the fact she
OL,11,Ftook cocaine and drank a lot of
OL,12,Falcohol.
OL,14,FIn September 2021, while Clark, of
OL,15,FEnots Close, Lichfield, was pregnant,
OL,16,FJefferson sent her a message
OL,17,Fthreatening to "put you 6ft
OL,18,Funderground" if she killed her baby
OL,19,Fthrough drinking.
OL,26,@oD@\OUpD@OO]yD@POUzD@LO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
