SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776442271
OL,3,CParents jailed over death of five-week-
OL,4,Cold baby with 40 rib fractures
OL,6,FJefferson was also a drug user,
OL,7,Fsmoking cannabis in the garage during
OL,8,Fa "volatile" relationship said to be
OL,9,Fcharacterised by consistent arguments
OL,10,Fand aggression.
OL,12,FDefence counsel for Clark, Tom
OL,13,FWalkling KC, said of the mother:
OL,14,F"She's herself a victim of Sean
OL,15,FJefferson's offending. She is a mother
OL,16,Fwhose baby was murdered by someone
OL,17,Felse.
OL,26,@pD@COUpD@LO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
